                    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button">Read about training and talks</button>
                    <h4><strong>I am a father and husband</strong></h4>
                    <p>I live with my family in Jaali, where I have served as chair of the local residents association for several years. I am a bibliophile, food enthusiast, road-traveller, and a renovator of a 1970s house. [Read more]</p>
